org.apache.hadoop.yarn.api.protocolrecords
Interface GetApplicationReportRequest

@InterfaceAudience.Public
@InterfaceStability.Stable
public interface GetApplicationReportRequest

The request sent by a client to the ResourceManager to get an ApplicationReport for an application.

The request should include the ApplicationId of the application.

See Also:
ClientRMProtocol.getApplicationReport(GetApplicationReportRequest), ApplicationReport
